What are arrays used for?
Arrays are used to group variables.
What is the code for an int array?
int[] arrayStuff;
What is the code for an String array?
String[] arrayStuff;
What is the code for an boolean array?
boolean[] arrayStuff;
What is the code for an double array?
doulbe[] arrayStuff;
How would you change the first value of the int array to 42?
arrayStuff[0] = 42;
Of the String array to "Bob"?
arrayStuff[0] = "Bob";
What does this do: private String[] dessert = new String[3];
makes a private string for dessert.
What does this do: private String[] postres = {"rice pudding", "pan dulce", "bu$
Makes a private string with the three idetities listed in the curly brackets
How are they different?
One has various values assigned to it, the other just makes space for 3 strings.
How would we replace "bunuelos" with "apple pie"?
private String[] postres = {"rice pudding", "pan dulce", "apple pie"};

